= ⬡ QUARTER III GATHERING — The Long Work Begun

*Theme:* Group witnessing of long circulations; sharing the inner work of Quarter III.

#hm-note[
  The witnessing of sealed circulations at this gathering carries operative weight.
  Each student names their preparation, its contents, its intention, and its
  minimum duration. The group holds this in awareness together. This is not a
  performance — it is the alchemical equivalent of signing the Oath in the
  presence of witnesses. Take it seriously.
]

*Students share:*
- The preparation they have sealed for long circulation: what is in it, why they
  chose it, and what they intend.
- Their somatic awareness practice from Month 8: what they have discovered about
  the three principles within themselves.
- One reading from the Golden Chain Book II that has most struck them this
  quarter, and why.

